  "raw_response": "Certainly! Below is a single HTML file that creates a fully functional Kanban board with the specified requirements. It uses vanilla JavaScript for functionality, Tailwind CSS via CDN for styling, and includes a confetti animation when cards are moved to the \"Done\" column.\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Kanban Board</title>\n    <!-- Tailwind CSS via CDN -->\n    <link href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        .confetti {\n            position: fixed;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            pointer-events: none;\n            z-index: 9999;\n        }\n        .card {\n            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-gray-100 p-6\">\n    <div id=\"kanban-board\" class=\"flex space-x-4\">\n        <!-- Backlog Column -->\n        <div id=\"backlog\" data-testid=\"column-backlog\" class=\"w-1/4 bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\">Backlog</h2>\n            <div id=\"backlog-cards\" class=\"space-y-4\"></div>\n            <button data-testid=\"add-card\" class=\"mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-600 focus:outline-none\">Add card</button>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-- In Progress Column -->\n        <div id=\"in-progress\" data-testid=\"column-in-progress\" class=\"w-1/4 bg-white p-4 rounded shadow-lg\">\n            <h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold mb-4\">In Progress</h2>\n            <div id=\"in-progress-cards\" class=\"space-y-4\"></div>\n            <button data-testid=\"add-card\" class=\"mt-4 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded hover:bg-blue-600 focus:outline-none\">Add card</button>\n        </div>\n\n        <!-